    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle of Decay: Survival</strong> 是一款轻量、偏街机节奏的俯视角波次生存游戏，背景设定在爆发期间。可单人或 1–4 人合作游玩，解锁区域、武装自己，坚守住感染者的进攻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133620/extras/1596d4bfd386ef9c8c565db514baf5a2.poster.avif?t=1755528408\" width=620 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133620/extras/1596d4bfd386ef9c8c565db514baf5a2.webm?t=1755528408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133620/extras/1596d4bfd386ef9c8c565db514baf5a2.mp4?t=1755528408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>波次猛攻，提供可选的头部锁定自动瞄准激光</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为什么选择 BoD:S？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >干脆利落的俯视射击，通过区域、天赋和可升级武器带来清晰的成长——一切都以街机节奏推进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133620/extras/98b854019f658bc80598b3be16da0059.poster.avif?t=1755528408\" width=620 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133620/extras/98b854019f658bc80598b3be16da0059.webm?t=1755528408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133620/extras/98b854019f658bc80598b3be16da0059.mp4?t=1755528408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>利用防御物与炮台，尽可能长时间守住阵地</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>模式</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>剧情（合作）：</strong> 杀出医院、地下区域与城市。解锁新区段、找到密码，撑过一波又一波。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无尽生存（合作或机器人）：</strong> 竞技场式地图，包含可购买区段、神秘/周边箱、递增波次、可放置防御、升级与排行榜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>模组/创意工坊：</strong> 早期支持 Steam 创意工坊，欢迎社区地图。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133620/extras/ccf2470712ab1140d6426c2ec0768bd6.poster.avif?t=1755528408\" width=620 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133620/extras/ccf2470712ab1140d6426c2ec0768bd6.webm?t=1755528408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133620/extras/ccf2470712ab1140d6426c2ec0768bd6.mp4?t=1755528408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>开门、找到密码便签，并完成快速布线/输入类小游戏以扩展地图</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>感染者变种：</strong> 普通、疾跑、重装，以及抱抱者（抓取）与喷吐者（遮挡视野），配有快速反制提示——并有离波次的小型首领遭遇。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>区段与经济：</strong> 通过击杀与修复获取点数，用于购买弹药、开门、解锁区域与抽神秘/周边箱。获取 XP 以解锁更多武器与功能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可升级武器与天赋：</strong> 提升伤害、弹匣容量、射速等；选择天赋如更高生命、更快装填或额外武器栏位。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>装备与可放置物：</strong> 携带主武器与装备（手雷、燃烧瓶、眩晕、诱饵）。用可移动路障、自动炮台、弹药箱与医疗包加固。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>防弹衣与团队配合：</strong> 防弹衣提升生存力与团队效用（如更快救援）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>风格与竞赛：</strong> 排行榜与外观商店（皮肤、激光颜色、发光鞋、弹药/效果颜色）。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133620/extras/debc62a14920ff54c9787b8b2e75c9ac.poster.avif?t=1755528408\" width=620 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133620/extras/debc62a14920ff54c9787b8b2e75c9ac.webm?t=1755528408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133620/extras/debc62a14920ff54c9787b8b2e75c9ac.mp4?t=1755528408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>升级武器并选择天赋，匹配你的游玩风格</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>抢先体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们正在积极扩展 BoD:S：更多地图（医院、地堡、地铁、城市）、新的敌人组合、易用性改进以及更深入的模组支持。你的反馈将直接影响开发——欢迎随时提出建议 :) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133620/extras/500dc87298ddf391086b9a9a1e9a6467.poster.avif?t=1755528408\" width=620 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133620/extras/500dc87298ddf391086b9a9a1e9a6467.webm?t=1755528408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133620/extras/500dc87298ddf391086b9a9a1e9a6467.mp4?t=1755528408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>抱抱者与喷吐者——迅速反制，否则会被淹没</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>愿望单与反馈</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>将 BoD:S 加入愿望单</strong>，并告诉我们需要改进的地方——一起打磨爆发体验！</p>",
